(In reply to Mark Johnston from comment #3)
Might be the e820 or EFI metadata is somewhat erroneous?  Just speculating at this point.  phys_segs should help.

@Rafael, bootverbose mode should print out the BIOS or EFI metadata we use for understanding physical memory layout before the panic.  12.1 may print the same information, but I'm not sure.  And thanks for the report, and your help investigating!
